1258
01:16:43,940 --> 01:16:45,380
Hye Kyo mi zavolala.

1259
01:16:47,750 --> 01:16:50,050
Aj ona vie, aký som.

1260
01:16:51,050 --> 01:16:52,150
Povedala,

1261
01:16:53,090 --> 01:16:56,310
"Viem že sa nemáš dobre
a obviňuješ sa."

1262
01:16:56,310 --> 01:16:57,740
(Telefonát Hye Kyo telefonát
ho veľmi potešil).

