1286
01:18:19,420 --> 01:18:20,480
Nazvi to rybou.

1287
01:18:20,880 --> 01:18:21,950
Je to rybacie.

1288
01:18:23,280 --> 01:18:25,380
Ty si decko. Ty si také decko.

